{"name": "search-engine-tool-vito1317", "metadata": {"name": "search-engine-tool-vito1317", "version": "0.7.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11"], "home_page": "https://github.com/vito1317/search-engine-tool-vito1317", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["selenium", "BeautifulSoup4"], "summary": "\u641c\u7d22\u5f15\u64ceAPI Bing / Google / Yahoo", "upload_time": 1731491516}, "documentation": ["# \u9805\u76ee\u8aaa\u660e\nhttps://github.com/vito1317/search-engine-tool-vito1317\n\n\u9805\u76ee\u7684 Python \u7248\u672c\u3002\u539f\u9805\u76ee\u4f7f\u7528 Node + Puppeteer\uff0cPython \u7248\u672c\u4f7f\u7528 Selenium + requests + BeautifulSoup4\u3002\n### \u6b64\u641c\u7d22\u5f15\u64ceApi\u7531 vito \u67ef\u744b\u5bb8\u767c\u5e03\n## \u5b89\u88dd\n```bash\npip install search-engine-tool-vito1317\n```\n# \u4f7f\u7528 \n```python \nfrom search_engine_tool_vito1317 import google\ndef test_google():\n    try: data = google.search(\"\u53f0\u7063\u5929\u6c23\") \n        for d in data: \n            print(d) \n    except Exception as e: \n        print(e) \nif __name__ == '__main__': \n    test_google() \n```\n# \u4f7f\u7528 request\n```python \nfrom search_engine_tool_vito1317 import google\ndef test_google():\n    try: data = google.search(\"\u53f0\u7063\u5929\u6c23\", \"request\") \n        for d in data: \n            print(d) \n    except Exception as e: \n        print(e) \nif __name__ == '__main__': \n    test_google() \n```\n# \u8fd4\u56de\u683c\u5f0f \n```json\n[ \n    {\n    \"abstract\": \"Web\u76ee\u524d\u5929\u6c23. PM2:04. 84\u00b0 F. RealFeel\u00ae 93\u00b0. RealFeel Shade\u2122 89\u00b0. \u7a7a\u6c23\u54c1\u8cea \u4e0d\u4f73. \u98a8 \u897f\u5357\u504f\u897f 6\u82f1\u91cc/\u5c0f\u65f6. \u98a8\u901f 6\u82f1\u91cc/\u5c0f\u65f6. \u9670 \u66f4\u591a\u8a73\u60c5.\",\n    \"href\": \"https://www.accuweather.com/zh/cn/shenzhen/58194/weather-forecast/58194\",\n    \"title\": \"\u53f0\u7063, \u53f0\u5317\u5e02, \u53f0\u7063 \u4e09\u65e5\u5929\u6c23\u9810\u5831 | AccuWeather\" \n}, \n... ]\n``` \n# \u652f\u6301\u641c\u5c0b\u5f15\u64ce \n```\nBing Google (\u9700\u8981\u8abf\u9069\u65b9\u81ea\u8eab\u80fd\u5920\u8a2a\u554f) Yahoo \n```\n# Todo \n ``` \n 1 \u8655\u7406\u4eba\u6a5f\u9a57\u8b49\n 2 \u652f\u6301\u7ffb\u9801\u53c3\u6578\n 3 wikipedia \u652f\u6301\n```\n \n # search-engine-tool-vito1317\n"], "modules": [{"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.search_engine_tool", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.search_engine_tool.searchEngineTool", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "keyword", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "engine", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "config", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine.bing", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine.bing.search", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "keyword", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "config", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine.bing", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine.yahoo", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine.google", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine.bing", "xref": {"fqname": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine..bing", "project": null}}, {"name": "search_engine_tool_vito1317.engine.google", "xref": {"fqn